4
00:00:32,700 --> 00:00:36,250
<i>Episode 7</i>

5
00:00:36,250 --> 00:00:39,130
<i>Prosecutor, please question the accused.</i>

6
00:00:44,030 --> 00:00:50,320
<i>Why did you follow the victim all the way to her blind date and disturb their date?</i>

7
00:00:50,320 --> 00:00:52,420
