75
00:07:02,770 --> 00:07:06,920
♫ <i>Our everlasting moments, and shared feelings</i> ♫

76
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:12,750
♫ <i>I promise you, they won't change</i> ♫

77
00:07:14,660 --> 00:07:16,460
Well,

78
00:07:18,270 --> 00:07:22,350
